:24.000Z","msg":"求其公開一樣倉底貨技術都輾壓支那自煮燃發嘅最新科技<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94a4f77ef2349829c371ddbbbab40ac6069f5159","tid":975270,"uid":59511,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"3e8d956e05f83ceb112711430f2c749d8bb32da9","tid":975270,"uid":44454,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T13:38:11.000Z","msg":"美軍：你唔發表電磁炮，我咪唔發表高速彈囉"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T14:20:11.000Z","msg":"電磁炮係美軍十鳩幾年前研究軍用，最後覺得呢個技術好難應用先腰斬。<br />\n我估應該係電磁炮雖然平均成本低，但戰時要連續發射點樣提供足夠而持續嘅電力先係大問題。<br />\n就好似之前出嚟扮晒野嘅牆角槍咁，係以色列發明完連自己都唔用嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大陸拎嚟打飛機。<br />\n把野裝彈少，負重高，打淨止嘅目標先有見得人嘅命中率<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2526751486d1e4ce5d3457741cc525964646d03e","tid":975270,"uid":2654,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"02c4d661169424b60fbaec079fe8c768fc1c30fd","tid":975270,"uid":28451,"like":35,"dislike":1,"score":34,"quote":{"pid":"8fd40be85c9de003a817cc758d97d416f912a2bd","tid":975270,"uid":32782,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T13:46:23.000Z","msg":"你老味，唔講真係唔知射一炮成本咁撚貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T13:52:47.000Z","msg":"一層層樓咁射出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T14:23:17.000Z","msg":"呢粒算平 之前DDG-1000個粒貴到可以買豪宅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 連美帝自己都貴到頂唔順<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77570f3116c9dffa0ed48bca0d612d2bde82d6aa","tid":975270,"uid":11973,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T14:38:48.000Z","msg":"即係話緊俾你聽<br />\n喺美國佬眼中電磁砲呢味嘢已經落後唔玩喇<br />\n另外美國佬講得出嚟俾你知即係已經唔係新嘢<br />\n隨時收埋大把更強更癡線嘅武器<br />\n莫講話望車尾燈<br />\n聲你都分分鐘聽唔到"},{"pid":"d4363ed0a24e936ab55ae91e092f03c240574d8c","tid":975270,"uid":52595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re